==============================
	HbbTV Development Kit
==============================

version: 0.0.1

hdk	|- build	// build directory for compile
	|- include	// HDK interfaces
	|- libs		// sub-libraries for HDK
	|- main		// HDK main module
	|- plugins	// HDK plugins

==============================
	How to Build
==============================
* compile & install to out folder
	$ cd build
	$ make

==============================
	HDK library
==============================
* libhdk.a
 - HbbTV Development Kit

* libsedec.so
 - Section Codec Library 
